sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Desktop App<br/>(Tauri + React)
    participant AAD as Azure AD<br/>(login.microsoftonline.com)
    participant API as Backend API<br/>(FastAPI)
    participant TV as AzureADTokenValidator
    participant JWKS as Azure AD JWKS<br/>(Public Keys)
    participant AU as AuthorizedUsersStore<br/>(authorized_users.yml)
    participant Perms as Permissions<br/>(Roles & Countries)

    Note over App,AAD: 1. Login (handled by MSAL in desktop app)
    App->>AAD: OAuth2 Authorization Code Flow
    AAD-->>App: JWT access_token (RS256 signed)

    Note over App,API: 2. API Request with Bearer Token
    App->>API: GET /trigger (Authorization: Bearer {jwt})

    Note over API,Perms: 3. Token Validation Pipeline
    API->>TV: validate(token)

    TV->>TV: Decode header, extract 'kid'

    alt JWKS cache valid (< 24h)
        TV->>TV: Use cached public keys
    else JWKS cache expired or kid not found
        TV->>JWKS: GET /discovery/v2.0/keys
        JWKS-->>TV: JWKS key set (RSA public keys)
        TV->>TV: Cache keys (TTL: 24h)
    end

    TV->>TV: jwt.decode(token, public_key, RS256)
    Note over TV: Verify: signature, exp, iss, aud, oid

    alt Token invalid or expired
        TV-->>API: InvalidTokenError
        API-->>App: 401 Unauthorized
    else Token valid
        TV-->>API: AzureADTokenClaims(email, name, oid, tid)
    end

    Note over API,Perms: 4. Authorization Check
    API->>AU: get_user(email)

    alt User not in allowlist
        AU-->>API: None
        API-->>App: 403 Forbidden (not authorized)
    else User found
        AU-->>API: AuthorizedUser(email, roles, countries)
    end

    API->>Perms: Check role permissions
    Note over Perms: Roles: admin, operator, viewer
    Perms->>Perms: is_admin? can_trigger_sync? can_access_country?

    alt Permission denied
        Perms-->>API: Forbidden
        API-->>App: 403 Forbidden (insufficient permissions)
    else Permission granted
        Perms-->>API: Authorized
        API-->>App: 200 OK (response data)
    end
